BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[FFXIV] Valentione's Day Comes to Eorzea on February 2!
DTSTART:20260202T000000Z
DTEND:20260216T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260311T062322Z
UID:64a388998406@mmo-calendar
DESCRIPTION:The season of ardor and affection is come again\, and as per c
 ustom\, cities and residential areas the realm over are set to be festoone
 d with romantic decorations. In Gridania\, the emissaries of love\, Astrid
  de Valentione and Emilie\, are preparing a spread of sumptuous cakes─pr
 ovided their mammet-assisted supply chain doesn't encounter any unexpected
  issues...\n\nRead on for details.
URL:https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/topics/detail/44ac60147d36ae9
 974713f75a61cca2eb2b9f2c0
